<div class="jumbotron text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/" class="lang-logo">
      <img src="/lang-logo.png">
    </a>
    <h1>Can I even web?</h1>
    <p>This is a simple Node application deployed to Heroku<br/>This is a simple app &ndash; 'cause it's my first time and I knew nothing about any of this</p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <ul id="tabnav" class="nav nav-pills hidden">
    <li><a data-toggle="pill" href="#photo">Photo</a></li>
    <li><a data-toggle="pill" href="#album">Album</a></li>
    <li class="active"><a data-toggle="pill" href="#gallery">Gallery</a></li>
